    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require travel companies & airlines to pay compensation if no refund in 14 days",
        "additional_details": "In difficult times for everyone, people are relying on the money that travel companies are holding onto, they are breaking the law and need to be held to account.  They should be compensating people who have not been refunded within 14 days.",
        "background": "Travel Companies and airlines are deliberately breaking the law and not refunding people for well over 5 weeks, not answering questions or replying to emails.",
